metadata.name: schusgi
metadata.description: My comic character called 'Schusgi' and that I created personally in my own childhood. This is the original Schusgi look.
metadata.Best of my Jokes: I believe that AI bots are actually in reality large centers of human workforce staff that perform prompted tasks manually over the Internet. Now with that in mind, imagine someone from that center being in charge of supporting intelligent services of an electronic toothbrush and its app. This will require that someone to look very closely at the webcam live while you are brushing your teeth. Only that way he or she can highlight to your app that any teeth got missed and hence are left uncleansed :-D - MK, May 2023
metadata.Special Benefit: First schusgi NFT ever in history
